Files derived from codex-plugin-cc:
    src/lib/codex/        (app-server.ts, process.ts, protocol.ts, turn.ts, auth.ts)
    tests/fake-codex.mjs

Modifications made by harry:
    - Ported from JavaScript (.mjs) to TypeScript.
    - Removed the broker transport entirely; Codex runs via the direct
      spawned `codex app-server` transport only.
    - Added token_count / rate-limits handling (rate_limits primary/secondary
      used-percent, plan type, reset time, last token usage) that the source
      did not surface.
    - Added a connect/initialize timeout that tears down the spawned child,
      so a turn cannot hang the host process.
    - Trimmed to the subset needed by harry's ask/review/fix commands.
